[center][color=pink][u][b][font=Tahoma][size=6]Introduction[/size][/font][/b][/u][/color][u]
[/u][font=Comic Sans MS]Hello! This is my first mod so please report any bugs! This will regularly be updated with presets every week until I reach 5 per human/elf races. I will not make any Argonian/Khajit as they are hard to alter from the base appearance. There is currently 3 presets, a Breton, High Elf and Redguard. More will come! Be sure to get all the required mods or they could turn out wrinkly and old![/font]
[color=pink][b][size=6][u][font=Tahoma]Requirements[/font][/u][/size][u]
[/u][/b][/color][font=Comic Sans MS]RaceMenu
SKSE
CBBE 
Freckle Mania
The Eyes of Beauty
HDT Ks Hairdos
HDT Physics 
KS Hairdos Highlights/Multi Colored Hair HDT version (optional) 
Brows (via Steam)
SG Female Textures Renewal 
[color=pink][b][u][size=6][font=Tahoma]Installation [/font][/size]
[/u][/b][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][/color]Download manually, go to your Skyrim folder location, data, skse, plugins, CharGen, presets and drop the .jslot files there. Then load in game with RaceMenu!
